ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This class covers both history and historiography in an enlightening way. Professor Sorkin is amazing
This course is one part history and one part historiography. It not only teaches you about the events of the modern period, it also orients you to recent scholarly trends. Highly recommended!

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I used my paper for this course to review the literature relevant to an area I am planning to work on for my dissertation. The course was very helpful for this.
